{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, of course, [GERMAN] was-- which we didn't know-- came from the name of [GERMAN], who was the-- who was the protector the German-- protector of in Czechoslovakia, in Prague.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was basically a deputy of Himmler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was active in anti-Jewish acts, sins, before the war even.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was assassinated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was killed by British agents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in his honor, so to say, they planned the action of extermination in [POLISH], all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was really a group unit, which came to Warsaw in July, '42.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they started the deportation action, which we called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We called it action.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it started, really, on the 22nd of July, '42.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it started immediately by-- I mean, there were already 19th, 20th, 21, everything, it was obvious that something was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "On 22nd, I think, everywhere the posters were put, everywhere, about [GERMAN], about transportation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is not exactly transportation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were all the [GERMAN], and all of their families, the Jewish police and their families, the doctors and the workers in the hospital and their families, the workers in the shops working for the German industry, or for the German army and their families, [INAUDIBLE] and their families, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were quite a lot of categories of people who were to be spared from the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As for the rest, they had to appear with their things, with a small amount of things because they couldn't take so much, and with some basic requirements, and clothes, and so on, on the [GERMAN], which was the kind of train siding in the north end of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, they are going to be transported to the east.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
